title: Gigantic, Luxurious 1 Bed Townhome
posting_body: Surrounded by mature trees with a location in a master-planned Northwest Hills neighborhood, one bedroom townhome for rent in a community with the suburban-style comforts you crave.
Luxe amenities and features deliver total satisfaction.
When you’re not taking advantage of everything at home, quick access to the MoPac and Route 183 makes it easy to reach your favorite Austin, TX, destinations.
After a day shopping at The Domain or enjoying the nearby outdoor recreation, return home to a pet-friendly townhome with nine-foot ceilings and elegant crown molding.
Newly remodeled, features wood-style flooring, as well as updated kitchen with a full suite of Energy Star-certified stainless steel appliances.
Oversized closet, in-home washer and dryer set and attached patio enhance the comfort and convenience throughout your home.
You have to see this place for yourself!
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
